教區範圍位於[[卡坦扎羅省|卡坦扎羅省]]西北部，2004年有教友139,400人，佔轄區總人口99.6%。教區下轄六十個堂區，有六十九名司鐸。

現任教區主教為{{link-it|若瑟·斯基拉奇|Giuseppe Schillaci}}，榮休主教為{{link-it|類斯·安多尼·坎塔福拉|Luigi Antonio Cantafora}}。<ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 03.05.2019 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/05/03/190503b.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-08-10 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190810150917/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/05/03/190503b.html |archivedate=2019-08-10 |language=en |date=2019-05-03 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

